### Positive numbers
POST http://localhost:8080/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": 5,
  "number2": 3
}

### Negative numbers
POST http://localhost:8080/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": -10,
  "number2": -7
}

### Zero and positive number
POST http://localhost:8080/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": 0,
  "number2": 15
}

### Large numbers
POST http://localhost:8080/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": 1000000,
  "number2": 2000000
}

### Floating point numbers (note: these will be truncated to integers)
POST http://localhost:8080/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number1": 3.14,
  "number2": 2.86
}
